precis:
Regulations Amending the APPLICATION OF PROVINCIAL LAWS REGULATIONS by
treating all vehicular parking, standing or stopping violations that
occur on any federal property in Ontario as having been committed in a
municipality designated under the Provincial Offences Act of Ontario.
